uments</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1109,184,'_product_features','field_55809dbfeeb63'),(1110,184,'additional_options',''),(1111,184,'_additional_options','field_55809f397125f'),(1112,185,'_edit_lock','1438638382:3'),(1113,185,'_edit_last','3'),(1114,185,'product_features','<ul>\r\n	<li>Outer housing: stainless steel, material 1.4301, surface brushed</li>\r\n	<li>Inner housing: stainless steel, material 1.4301, surface electro-polished</li>\r\n	<li>Working chamber: clean room class ISO 7 acc. to DIN EN ISO 14644-1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Special Features</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>GMP/FDA-compliant design with qualification</li>\r\n	<li>S!MPAC control system with 8’ color touch panel</li>\r\n	<li>PC-Software S!MPATI PHARMA FDA 21 CFR Part 11</li>\r\n	<li>Cascade control system with flexible sensor</li>\r\n	<li>1-channel line printer</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1115,185,'_product_features','field_55809dbfeeb63'),(1116,185,'additional_options',''),(1117,185,'_additional_options','field_55809f397125f'),(1118,186,'_edit_lock','1438631287:3'),(1119,186,'_edit_last','3'),(1120,186,'product_features','<ul>\r\n	<li>Outer housing: stainless steel, material 1.4301, surface brushed</li>\r\n	<li>Inner housing: stainless steel, material 1.4301, surface electro-polished</li>\r\n	<li>12 levels available with GMP compliant charging trays</li>\r\n	<li>HEPA exhaust air filter</li>\r\n	<li>Fresh air filter F7</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Special Features</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>GMP/FDA-compliant design with qualification</li>\r\n	<li>Transport of oven possible due to under running bottom section</li>\r\n	<li>Speed-controlled recirculation air fan</li>\r\n	<li>Speed-controlled fresh air fan</li>\r\n	<li>Adjustment of air flow within working chamber</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1121,186,'_product_features','field_55809dbfeeb63'),(1122,186,'additional_options',''),(1123,186,'_additional_options','field_55809f397125f'),(1124,187,'_edit_lock','1438631195:3'),(1125,187,'_edit_last','3'),(1126,187,'product_features','<ul>\r\n	<li>Inner casing (seal-welded) and outer casing of stainless steel (1.4301)</li>\r\n	<li>Automatic charging trolley transfer to cooling chamber</li>\r\n	<li>Program automation</li>\r\n	<li>3 electro-motive driven vertical lift-doors</li>\r\n	<li>Photoelectric transfer monitoring</li>\r\n	<li>HOSCH filter</li>\r\n	<li>Switch cabinet, separate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Special Features</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Clean room conditions in effective space VDI 2083, Class 3</li>\r\n	<li>Sterilizing and cooling in separate chambers, therefore shorter processing times</li>\r\n	<li>During the cooling phase, a further charge can be sterilized</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1127,187,'_product_features','field_55809dbfeeb63'),(1128,187,'additional_options',''),(1129,187,'_additional_options','field_55809f397125f'),(1136,189,'_edit_lock','1437597187:3'),(1137,189,'_edit_last','3'),(1138,189,'product_features','<ul>\r\n	<li>The volume of flammable substances that can be introduced is virtually unlimited. The heating and drying ovens comply with category 2 devices and can thus be installed in zones 1 and 2 of areas where there is a danger of explosion.</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible design in compliance with device group ll, i. e. suitable for solvents of temperature classes T1, T2, T3, T4 and explosion groups llA and llB.</li>\r\n	<li>Warm water or steam emitted from processes can be used as a heating medium. Low energy consumption and short process times with circulating air and low fresh air volume.</li>\r\n	<li>High constancy of temperature within the entire work chamber.</li>\r\n	<li>For installing in explosive zones, all components are explosion resistant according to the respective zone. Fresh air required for safe and reliable operation must be supplied from a neutral zone</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Accessories</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Temperature conditioning</li>\r\n	<li>Devices</li>\r\n	<li>Fresh air grid</li>\r\n	<li>Exhaust air fan</li>\r\n	<li>Door window</li>\r\n	<li>Shelves and grids</li>\r\n	<li>Charging trolleys</li>\r\n	<li>Flow control valves</li>\r\n	<li>Condensate collector</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Special Constructions</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Heat treatment processes in inert gas atmosphere</li>\r\n	<li>Processes under clean room conditions</li>\r\n	<li>Drying of explosive substances</li>\r\n	<li>Solvent recovery</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1139,189,'_product_features','field_55809dbfeeb63'),(1140,189,'additional_options',''),(1141,189,'_additional_options','field_55809f397125f'),(1142,190,'_edit_lock','1436980915:3'),(1143,190,'_edit_last','3'),(1144,190,'product_features','<ul>\r\n	<li>Inner housing made of stainless steel (material no. 1.4301) in compliance with GMP</li>\r\n	<li>Outer housing made of stainless steel (material no. 1.4301), polished surface (grain 400)</li>\r\n	<li>Charging with trolley and auxiliary trolley</li>\r\n	<li>Hot water tempering device 140 °C</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Special Features</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Surface roughness &lt; 0.8 µm</li>\r\n	<li>Installation in a clean room of Class ISO 7 (DIN EN ISO 14644-1)</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1145,190,'_product_features','field_55809dbfeeb63'),(1146,190,'additional_options',''),(1147,190,'_additional_options','field_55809f397125f'),(1148,191,'_edit_lock','1436980704:3'),(1149,191,'_edit_last','3'),(1150,191,'product_features','<ul>\r\n	<li>Explosion resistant interior, class of temperature T3, zone 1</li>\r\n	<li>Outer casing made of electronically galvanized sheet steel, coated (RAL 1015)</li>\r\n	<li>Interior made of aluminum coated sheet steel, welded tight</li>\r\n	<li>Door with window</li>\r\n	<li>Tubular lead-throughs in side walls</li>\r\n	<li>Vapor/air heat exchanger PN 16</li>\r\n	<li>Air circulating fan as per VDMA 24169</li>\r\n	<li>Temperature controller TC incl. RS 232/485 interface</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Special Features</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Steam-control valve, motor-operated</li>\r\n	<li>Safety cut-out</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1151,191,'_product_features','field_55809dbfeeb63'),(1152,191,'additional_options',''),(1153,191,'_additional_options','field_55809f397125f'),(1154,192,'_edit_lock','1436980649:3'),(1155,192,'_edit_last','3'),(1156,192,'product_features','<ul>\r\n	<li>Outer housing made of galvanized steel sheet</li>\r\n	<li>Interior housing made of stainless steel (material no. 1.4301)</li>\r\n	<li>Heating with saturated steam 4 bar overpressure</li>\r\n	<li>Interior according to device group II, category 2G</li>\r\n	<li>Outer device according to device group II, category 3G</li>\r\n	<li>Charging trolleys for charging trays, which can be docked to the drying oven.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Special Features</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Execution as per ATEX Directives 94/9/EC</li>\r\n	<li>12 pieces of inserts with direct steam heating</li>\r\n	<li>Air exchange through natural convection</li>\r\n	<li>Goods temperature control</li>\r\n	<li>Electro-pneumatic steam control valve in ex protection execution</li>\r\n	<li>Pressure shock resistant switch box</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1157,192,'_product_features','field_55809dbfeeb63'),(1158,192,'additional_options',''),(1159,192,'_additional_options','field_55809f397125f'),(1160,193,'_edit_lock','1439395219:3'),(1161,193,'_edit_last','3'),(1162,193,'product_features','<ul>\r\n	<li>The explosion resistant measures were examined by the “TÜV Nord CERT GmbH &amp; Co. KG”</li>\r\n	<li>For the purposes of assessment, the 94/9/EG (ATEX 95) regulations were applied. Weiss received the design certification</li>\r\n	<li>The units are designed for the performance of extreme climate values (e.g. long term tests at 85 °C/85 % RH).</li>\r\n	<li>Extreme installation conditions – trouble-free operation can be guaranteed at ambient temperatures of up to 35 °C.</li>\r\n	<li>Optimum air guidance and temperature distribution – better than ±1.5 K spatially guaranteed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Standard Version</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>CE-Certificate of design according to ATEX 95 (TÜV 10 ATEX 56193x)</li>\r\n	<li>Door contact switch with automatic lock</li>\r\n	<li>Door frame heater, explosion proof</li>\r\n	<li>Digital measuring and control system S!MPAC*</li>\r\n	<li>8“ TFT color touch panel, fitted at the front bracket</li>\r\n	<li>CONTROLPAD in the door for actual value display</li>\r\n	<li>Ethernet interface</li>\r\n	<li>USB interface</li>\r\n	<li>Condensation protection with dehumidifier coil to prevent condensation on the specimen</li>\r\n	<li>1 stainless steel port approx. 50 mm, positioned in left side wall</li>\r\n	<li>1 stainless steel port approx. 125 mm, positioned in right side wall</li>\r\n	<li>Digitally adjustable high/low temperature fuse with separate, intrinsically safe sensor</li>\r\n	<li>1 shelf (stainless steel)</li>\r\n	<li>Air-cooled refrigeration unit with environment-friendly refrigerants</li>\r\n	<li>Temperature controlled steam humidifier</li>\r\n	<li>Adjustable, vibration absorbing feet</li>\r\n	<li>Indirect heating of test space by heat transfer oil in a closed circuit</li>\r\n	<li>Temperature sensor intrinsically safe by isolation transformer</li>\r\n	<li>4 digital inputs and outputs</li>\r\n	<li>Specimen fuse and switch-off</li>\r\n	<li>Calibration of 2 temperature values (+23 °C and +80 °C)</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1163,193,'_product_features','field_55809dbfeeb63'),(1164,193,'additional_options','<ul>\r\n	<li>Self-cleaning psychometric humidity sensor</li>\r\n	<li>Condensate drain, closed by syphon</li>\r\n	<li>Water storage tank including level indicator and automatic water supply</li>\r\n	<li>Purging device for humidification and water</li>\r\n	<li>Calibration of 2 climate values (23 °C/50 % RH and 95 °C/50 % RH)</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1165,193,'_additional_options','field_55809f397125f'),(1166,194,'_edit_lock','1438635569:3'),(1167,194,'_edit_last','3'),(1168,194,'product_features','<ul>\r\n	<li>Heat-sensitive mediums (e. g. pharmaceutical products) are dried with care</li>\r\n	<li>Reduced drying times by lowering the pressure within the chamber</li>\r\n	<li>Due to the extremely low remaining oxygen content in the drying oven there are no oxidation processes</li>\r\n	<li>Evaporating fluids (e. g. solvents) can be recovered</li>\r\n	<li>Optimum drying conditions for light, powdery products as there is no convection</li>\r\n	<li>No “skin-forming” on the product being dried; thereby providing constant drying performance</li>\r\n	<li>Economic because steam or warm water from other processes can be used as a heat medium</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible heating</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Options/Accessories</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Use of special materials for all components that come into contact with evaporating fluids (e. g. Inconel, Hasteloy)</li>\r\n	<li>Combination with recirculation air for heating up of products at normal atmosphere</li>\r\n	<li>Design in accordance with GMP-/FDA</li>\r\n	<li>Qualification documents are issued as verification of our tests</li>\r\n	<li>In order to avoid condensation in the drying oven, the door and walls can be heated</li>\r\n	<li>Pneumatically-controlled doors for the automatic loading of the drying oven</li>\r\n	<li>Designed for high-vacuum processes</li>\r\n	<li>Special dimensions</li>\r\n	<li>Special vacuum pumps</li>\r\n	<li>S!MPATI* Software</li>\r\n	<li>Digital pressure display</li>\r\n	<li>Pressure control in conjunction with a solenoid valve in the suction line</li>\r\n	<li>Temperature sensor for product being dried</li>\r\n	<li>Nitrogen supply for quick extraction of released vapor</li>\r\n	<li>For aggressive solvents: door seals of viton or with FEP cover</li>\r\n	<li>External housing with surrounding frame for installation in wall</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1169,194,'_product_features','field_55809dbfeeb63'),(1170,194,'additional_options',''),(1171,194,'_additional_options','field_55809f397125f'),(1172,195,'_edit_lock','1438634157:3'),(1173,195,'_edit_last','3'),(1174,195,'product_features','<ul>\r\n	<li>Outer housing made of stainless steel, material no. 1.4301</li>\r\n	<li>Inner housing made of stainless steel, material no. 1.4571</li>\r\n	<li>Electrical external heatin