 protection) is provided by the complete topology (structure). This consists of:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>the metallic shell</li>\r\n	<li>electric lead-through (current, communication, antenna, signal cables)</li>\r\n	<li>mechanical lead-through (door, tubes, connector panel etc.)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Standard Version</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>User-friendly 3.5” TFT color touch panel</li>\r\n	<li>Digital measuring and control system Simpac</li>\r\n	<li>Simpati program tool on CD ROM for convenient programming of control via PC</li>\r\n	<li>Potential-free contact for switching off of test specimens</li>\r\n	<li>Independent, adjustable temperature limiter</li>\r\n	<li>Adjustable software temperature limiter min./max.</li>\r\n	<li>Ethernet interface</li>\r\n	<li>Air-cooled refrigeration unit</li>\r\n	<li>Calibration of 2 temperature values</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1484,245,'_product_features','field_55809dbfeeb63'),(1485,245,'additional_options','<ul>\r\n	<li>Software Simpati</li>\r\n	<li>Digital I/O</li>\r\n	<li>Interface RS 232</li>\r\n	<li>Interface IEEE 488</li>\r\n	<li>Networking (RS 485 interface)</li>\r\n	<li>Laboratory table, mobile (WxDxH 1000x750x720 mm)</li>\r\n	<li>Special voltages</li>\r\n	<li>Customized connector field, easily exchangeable</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1486,245,'_additional_options','field_55809f397125f'),(1487,248,'_edit_lock','1439404528:3'),(1488,248,'_edit_last','3'),(1489,248,'product_features','<ul>\r\n	<li>Dual air circulation system with solid stainless steel jack shafts</li>\r\n	<li>Nichrome wire heating elements with fail safe fusible link</li>\r\n	<li>Solid state heat switching</li>\r\n	<li>Full front opening door</li>\r\n	<li>Heavy duty hand wheel actuated door latching</li>\r\n	<li>8” thick walls</li>\r\n	<li>Internal pressure member</li>\r\n	<li>(EAH Models are constructed with an internal pressure member. EA</li>\r\n	<li>Models can be quoted with an external pressure member construction.)</li>\r\n	<li>Solid state altitude sensor</li>\r\n	<li>Interior light</li>\r\n	<li>ETL (UL STD 508A) approved main power panel</li>\r\n	<li>Instrumentation</li>\r\n	<li>Solutions Plus Programmer/Controller</li>\r\n	<li>Digital indication of set-point and temperature</li>\r\n	<li>Type “T” thermocouple sensor</li>\r\n	<li>RS232 and RS422 digital communications</li>\r\n	<li>Event or alarm outputs</li>\r\n	<li>Guaranteed soak and automatic hold</li>\r\n	<li>Refrigeration System</li>\r\n	<li>Water cooled condenser</li>\r\n	<li>Copper tubing cooling coils with aluminum fins</li>\r\n	<li>Cascade refrigeration system</li>\r\n	<li>High temperature silphosed or silver soldered joints</li>\r\n	<li>Semi-hermetic compressors</li>\r\n	<li>HFC refrigerants</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1490,248,'_product_features','field_55809dbfeeb63'),(1491,248,'additional_options','<ul>\r\n	<li>Stainless steel wire shelves</li>\r\n	<li>Heavy duty casters</li>\r\n	<li>Running time meter</li>\r\n	<li>Refrigeration gauges</li>\r\n	<li>Main power electrical disconnect switch</li>\r\n	<li>Low watt density sheath heaters for temperature control above 35,000 ft.</li>\r\n	<li>3” I.D. weld neck access port with insulating plug and blank flange</li>\r\n	<li>Refrigeration section quiet package</li>\r\n	<li>Dry air purge</li>\r\n	<li>Chart recorder</li>\r\n	<li>Custom sizes available consult with your local salesperson</li>\r\n	<li>Many options available - contact your local salesperson for complete list</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1492,248,'_additional_options','field_55809f397125f'),(1493,249,'_edit_lock','1438193969:3'),(1494,249,'_edit_last','3'),(1495,249,'product_features','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Weiss Envirotronics is a competent and experienced partner for planning and implementing the construction of drive-in altitude test chambers. Through cooperation with our customers and longstanding partners we can create the automotive test chamber tailored specifically to your needs.</span></p>'),(1496,249,'_product_features','field_55809dbfeeb63'),(1497,249,'additional_options',''),(1498