INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (8,2,'2015-06-10 17:52:35','2015-06-10 17:52:35','','Home','','publish','open','open','','home','','','2015-07-17 16:46:11','2015-07-17 16:46:11','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?page_id=8',23,'page','',0),(13,2,'2015-06-16 22:07:16','2015-06-16 22:07:16','','Product Features','','publish','closed','closed','','acf_product-features','','','2015-06-16 22:07:16','2015-06-16 22:07:16','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=acf&#038;p=13',0,'acf','',0),(14,2,'2015-06-16 22:12:30','2015-06-16 22:12:30','','Additional Options','','publish','closed','closed','','acf_additional-options','','','2015-06-16 22:12:30','2015-06-16 22:12:30','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=acf&#038;p=14',0,'acf','',0),(25,3,'2015-06-19 20:22:53','2015-06-19 20:22:53','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Our WK3-0 climate cabinet was designed to simulate long term and accelerated stability tests involving different climates and/or seasonal climates and the climatic zones of the world.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The specimens that have been exposed to long-term testing or accelerated service testing played a primary role throughout the development and construction process of the WK3-0.</span></p>','WK3-0','','publish','closed','closed','','wk3-0','','','2015-07-29 18:13:55','2015-07-29 18:13:55','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=25',193,'product','',0),(29,3,'2015-06-19 20:28:41','2015-06-19 20:28:41','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The TS-120 test chamber consists of two independently controlled chambers, one that is hot and one that is cold. The temperature shock between hot and cold is achieved thanks to the rapid transfer of the specimens on the lift and the subsequent exposure to a wide range of temperatures.</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;','TS-120','','publish','closed','closed','','ts-120','','','2015-08-10 20:48:23','2015-08-10 20:48:23','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=29',192,'product','',0),(31,3,'2015-06-19 20:31:00','2015-06-19 20:31:00','The pre-fabricated Walk-In/Drive-In test chamber\'s modular construction facilitates ease of move-in and setup. The WP Series accepts all sizes of Envirotronics roll-up conditioning modules. WP Series is suited for many Telcordia (Bellcore) applications.','WP/WPH','','publish','closed','closed','','wpwph','','','2015-08-03 19:16:03','2015-08-03 19:16:03','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=31',191,'product','',0),(35,3,'2015-06-19 20:34:13','2015-06-19 20:34:13','The pre-fabricated Walk-In/Drive-In test chamber\'s modular construction facilitates ease of move-in and setup. The WP Series accepts all sizes of Envirotronics roll-up conditioning modules. WP Series is suited for many Telcordia (Bellcore) applications.','Climate Chamber with Dynamometer','','publish','closed','closed','','climate-chamber-with-dynamometer','','','2015-07-27 21:22:31','2015-07-27 21:22:31','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=35',189,'product','',0),(44,3,'2015-06-19 21:35:04','2015-06-19 21:35:04','The WTS-3/WKS-3 test system is based on our tried and true modules, the WT and WK SERIES, now offer increased power for heating, cooling and circulating air. These chambers have volumes ranging from 190 to 1540 liters, and are capable of meeting virtually all requirements of contemporary ESS testing.','WTS-3/WK-3','','publish','closed','closed','','wts-3wk-3','','','2015-08-03 21:15:19','2015-08-03 21:15:19','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=44',190,'product','',0),(47,3,'2015-06-19 21:38:43','2015-06-19 21:38:43','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The TS-60 test chamber is made of two independently controlled chambers. One chamber is hot and the other one is cold. The temperature shock between hot and cold is created with the rapid transfer of the specimens on the lift and the subsequent exposure to a wide range of temperatures.</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;','TS-60','','publish','closed','closed','','ts-60-2','','','2015-08-10 19:21:03','2015-08-10 19:21:03','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=47',188,'product','',0),(49,3,'2015-06-19 21:39:45','2015-06-19 21:39:45','The STAR Plus(tm) System adds the dimensions of ease of use, consistency of performance, and total system reliability to your product development and/or production program.\r\n\r\nThe Envirotronics Star Plus System AGREE chambers are equipped with an LN2 cooling system. The LN2 cooling system, with modulating valve and directed airflow to the product, provides the rapid thermal change rates required to achieve maximum product stress. Additionally, these rates are accomplished with smaller space requirements, lower audible noise, no water requirement, and lower maintenance costs than a typical refrigeration system.\r\n\r\nThe chamber enclosure is insulated with sound dampening material to keep operating noise levels of the vibration equipment below 78dBa. Access to the chamber workspace is through large total-access doors.','STAR PLUS System','','publish','closed','closed','','star-plus-system-series-with-chamber','','','2015-08-11 17:10:01','2015-08-11 17:10:01','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=49',186,'product','',0),(50,3,'2015-06-19 21:40:15','2015-06-19 21:40:15','The STAR Plus Series vibration tables has one of the most consistent acceleration levels per unit area of any table on the market today thanks to it’s patented proprietary state of the art Six Degrees of Freedom, Tri-axial, Ppneumatic vibration tables. Among other benefits, when multiple products are tested they receive almost identical vibration forces regardless of where they are mounted. The vibration of the table is monitored and controlled by a tri-axial accelerometer block. The outputs of the three accelerometers are time multiplexed, producing and average gRMS level of all three axes. (Operational temperature range for accelerometer(s) is -51.1˚C to +107˚C)\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The table can be used separately from the chamber thanks to how readily the STAR Plus Series can be moved. With the “Easy Lift” actuator you can literally raise and lower the table with one finger. This duality means that the table can be used for one test, and the chamber used for a separate test, it’s like performing two tests at once!</span></p>','Star Series Vibration Tables','','publish','closed','closed','','star-plus-system-vibration-table','','','2015-08-11 17:05:06','2015-08-11 17:05:06','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=50',187,'product','',0),(51,3,'2015-06-19 21:40:38','2015-06-19 21:40:38','The Star Galaxy™ HALT/HASS systems are integrated test chamber/vibration table packages. These chambers are outfitted with a liquid nitrogen (LN2) cooling systems in order to provide the rapid thermal change rates required to achieve maximum product stress. The vibration table is a six degree-of-freedom (6DoF) tri-axial pneumatic vibration table.','Galaxy Series','','publish','closed','closed','','galaxy-series','','','2015-10-15 21:42:05','2015-10-15 21:42:05','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=51',185,'product','',0),(52,3,'2015-06-19 21:40:57','2015-06-19 21:40:57','<div class=\"fleft\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The EV series AGREE style chambers are available in sizes ranging from 12 to 110 cubic feet (340 L to 3114L), and accommodate electro-dynamic and mechanical vibration systems and/or roll-in product carts. The EV series can be used as a test chamber or as a test chamber with vibration tables.</span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"fleft\">Humidity option available</li>\r\n	<li class=\"fleft\">Vertical Lift option available</li>\r\n	<li class=\"fleft\">Custom sizes also available</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"fleft\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">These chambers allow for rapid temperature change rates and all systems are high pressure, leak tested, and operationally tested to performance specifications prior to delivery.</span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>','EV Series AGREE','','publish','closed','closed','','ev-series-agree','','','2015-08-03 19:06:00','2015-08-03 19:06:00','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=52',184,'product','',0),(54,3,'2015-06-19 21:42:20','2015-06-19 21:42:20','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Weiss Envirotronics pharmaceutical cabinet series is available in four sizes; the Pharma 280, 600, 1300 and 2000 all designed with durability in mind. Theses cabinets have been specifically developed to meet the requirement of testing facilities within the pharmaceutical industry. <strong>Also available in stock! <a href=\"http://envirotronics.com/in-stock-chambers-immediate-shipment\">click here</a></strong></span></p>','Stability Test Chambers','','publish','closed','closed','','stability-test-chambers','','','2015-10-02 19:46:16','2015-10-02 19:46:16','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=54',182,'product','',0),(56,3,'2015-06-19 22:02:43','2015-06-19 22:02:43','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The photo-stability test chambers, Pharma 250L Pharma 500L are characterized by ideal light, UV, temperature, and humidity distribution and can therefore guarantee a completely reproducible climate, UV and light conditions. The lighting equipment used in in compliance with the ICH guidelines, and Q1B Option 2 enables photo-stability tests to be carried out in less than 100 hours.</span></p>','Photo-stability Test Chambers','','publish','closed','closed','','photo-stability-test-chambers','','','2015-08-11 19:20:54','2015-08-11 19:20:54','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=56',183,'product','',0),(57,3,'2015-06-19 22:03:20','2015-06-19 22:03:20','Our climate cabinet VC³ 0 was designed to simulate different climates and/or seasonal climates and the climatic zones of the world, in particular for long-term and accelerated stability tests.\r\nThe specimens which have to be exposed to a long-term test and/or an accelerated service life test played a primary role throughout the entire development and construction process.','VC3 O','','publish','closed','closed','','stability-test-and-climate-cycling-chambers','','','2015-08-05 20:46:48','2015-08-05 20:46:48','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=57',180,'product','',0),(58,3,'2015-06-19 22:48:40','2015-06-19 22:48:40','ESS systems can be designed in reach-in or cart-based versions based on your requirements.\r\n\r\nThe ESS Series allows highly accelerated product temperature change rates through high air velocity conditioning. Due to the wide variety of products being tested, Weiss Envirotronics has developed standard models that feature either our patented horizontal or vertical air flow. Today\'s customer demands dictate that different temperature ranges as well as change rate capabilities to be offered. Weiss Envirotronics will equip your system with single-stage, cascade, twin-screw, LN2 boost, or LN2 cooled refrigeration systems. The powerful Weiss Envirotronics Solutions Plus(tm) Controller/Programmer is standard. By utilizing Quick Draw, we ensure that your product reaches set point as quickly as possible to reduce cycle times.\r\n\r\nThe tracks in the floor indicate that the chamber interior pictured above is a cart-based system. Also, the hole pattern in the side wall is characteristic of Weiss Envirotronics\' patented* high-velocity horizontal air flow system.\r\n\r\nWeiss Envirotronics will manufacture an ESS chamber to meet your specific environmental stress screening needs.','ESS Series','','publish','closed','closed','','ess-series','','','2015-08-10 21:31:36','2015-08-10 21:31:36','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=58',179,'product','',0),(59,3,'2015-06-19 22:49:05','2015-06-19 22:49:05','The ET27-1-10-WC-HAF test chamber was designed to maximize the testing capabilities for 19\" rack mountable networking equipment.\r\n\r\nIt was designed with right-to-left cross-chamber air flow to work with customer product by moving the air in the same direction as current customer-completed chassis designs. This helps to eliminate temperature gradients between upper and lower test tiers found in typical environmental chamber configurations. All chassis are exposed to identical temperature swings, changes, and ramp rates. Additionally, this system was designed with a single stage compressor system for ESS compatible product testing requirements between 0° and 50°C.\r\n\r\nThe ET27-1-10-WC-HAF Test Chamber\'s small size provides a much more flexible system by allowing more rapid load turn times and less impact during chamber down time for preventive maintenance.\r\n\r\nThe hole pattern in the side walls is characteristic of Envirotronics\' patented high-velocity horizontal air flow system.\r\n\r\nAll external connections typically found on other chamber designs such as water inlet/outlet and dry air purge systems have been moved inboard to protect them from accidental damage. Easy access for interconnect is provided through a 14\" x 12\" port which is conveniently located in the rear wall.','Model ET27-1-10-WC-HAF','','publish','closed','closed','','model-et27-1-10-wc-haf','','','2015-08-03 19:04:53','2015-08-03 19:04:53','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=59',181,'product','',0),(64,3,'2015-06-19 22:53:57','2015-06-19 22:53:57','The Star Galaxy™ HALT/HASS systems are integrated test chamber/vibration table packages. These chambers are outfitted with a liquid nitrogen (LN2) cooling systems in order to provide the rapid thermal change rates required to achieve maximum product stress. The vibration table is a six degree-of-freedom (6DoF) tri-axial pneumatic vibration table.','STAR GALAXY','','publish','closed','closed','','star-galaxy-2','','','2015-08-03 22:01:20','2015-08-03 22:01:20','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=64',178,'product','',0),(65,2,'2015-06-22 17:03:07','2015-06-22 17:03:07',' ','','','publish','open','open','','65','','','2015-08-11 21:08:37','2015-08-11 21:08:37','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?p=65',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(66,2,'2015-06-22 17:08:55','2015-06-22 17:08:55','','Products','','publish','open','open','','products','','','2015-06-22 17:08:55','2015-06-22 17:08:55','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?page_id=66',29,'page','',0),(67,2,'2015-06-22 17:09:31','2015-06-22 17:09:31',' ','','','publish','open','open','','67','','','2015-08-11 21:08:37','2015-08-11 21:08:37','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?p=67',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(69,2,'2015-06-22 17:28:52','2015-06-22 17:28:52',' ','','','publish','open','open','','69','','','2015-08-11 21:08:37','2015-08-11 21:08:37','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?p=69',7,'nav_menu_item','',0),(71,2,'2015-06-22 17:28:52','2015-06-22 17:28:52','','HALT/HASS/AGREE & Vibration','','publish','open','open','','halthassagree-vibration','','','2015-08-11 21:08:37','2015-08-11 21:08:37','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?p=71',8,'nav_menu_item','',0),(72,2,'2015-06-22 17:28:52','2015-06-22 17:28:52',' ','','','publish','open','open','','72','','','2015-08-11 21:08:37','2015-08-11 21:08:37','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?p=72',9,'nav_menu_item','',0),(73,2,'2015-06-22 17:28:52','2015-06-22 17:28:52',' ','','','publish','open','open','','73','','','2015-08-11 21:08:37','2015-08-11 21:08:37','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?p=73',10,'nav_menu_item','',0),(74,2,'2015-06-22 17:28:52','2015-06-22 17:28:52',' ','','','publish','open','open','','74','','','2015-08-11 21:08:37','2015-08-11 21:08:37','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?p=74',11,'nav_menu_item','',0),(75,2,'2015-06-22 17:28:52','2015-06-22 17:28:52',' ','','','publish'