c modules according to the standards IEC 61215 und IEC 61646. We provide also the suitable test chamber for temperature shock cycling tests, humidity freezing tests and damp heat tests.','Solar Technology Testing','','publish','closed','closed','','solar-technology-testing','','','2015-07-31 17:08:07','2015-07-31 17:08:07','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=150',163,'product','',0),(154,3,'2015-06-22 22:08:45','2015-06-22 22:08:45','The newly developed VHM HEPHAISTOS is an internationally patented system and characterized by a high field homogeneity. For the first time, the advantages of microwave technology have been developed successfully to an industrially mature high technology. The high field homogeneity allows for the manufacture of high-quality CFC aircraft structures, for instance.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Heating</li>\r\n	<li>Drying</li>\r\n	<li>Hardening</li>\r\n</ul>','Microwave Heating and Drying Cabinets VHM Hephaistos','','publish','closed','closed','','microwave-heating-and-drying-cabinets-vhm-hephaistos','','','2015-08-03 20:30:09','2015-08-03 20:30:09','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=154',162,'product','',0),(155,3,'2015-06-22 22:09:10','2015-06-22 22:09:10','Designed for hardening of fiber-reinforced composite structures and heating up of resin packages.','VHM 180/200','','publish','closed','closed','','vhm-180200','','','2015-08-03 20:29:27','2015-08-03 20:29:27','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=155',161,'product','',0),(156,3,'2015-06-22 22:09:47','2015-06-22 22:09:47','For the hardening of fiber composites and warming-up of resin.','VHM 100/100','','publish','closed','closed','','vhm-100100','','','2015-08-03 20:28:15','2015-08-03 20:28:15','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=156',160,'product','',0),(158,3,'2015-06-22 22:16:04','2015-06-22 22:16:04','For the heating of glass fiber strands prior to impregnation in liquid plastic and manufacture of glass fiber reinforced plastic granulate.','DZIR 300/10/110','','publish','closed','closed','','dzir-30010110','','','2015-08-11 21:06:10','2015-08-11 21:06:10','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=158',159,'product','',0),(160,3,'2015-06-22 22:18:07','2015-06-22 22:18:07','The WIBOjekt- and the WIBObarrier® system are the basic systems of all WIBO units. Especially shaped air outlets, so-called ejectors create a clean-air curtain that separates the work area and the surrounding area from each other safely.\r\n\r\nBy means of the clean-air curtain as separation between the product and the person, the WIBOjekt® principle protects the personnel and the room. Product dusts or gas releasing from the product are captured by means of the ejector air and led off specifically by the rear wall extraction.\r\n\r\nFor cases of application on which especially great importance is attached to stable protection of personnel and high clean-air quality in the product and work area, the WIBObarrier® system has been developed. All advantages of the WIBOjekt® system, such as protection of the person, room are combined.\r\n\r\nThe barrier clean-air curtain pulls along occurring particles from outside as well as from inside and transfers them to the extraction which is coordinated to that and which is located at the front side, on the rear side and on bottom level.\r\n\r\nWhile the laminar clean-air is flowing through the product area, the barrier clean-air curtain protects this area from air turbulences that are caused by the operating person.','WIBObarrier','','publish','closed','closed','','wibobarrier','','','2015-07-15 17:49:46','2015-07-15 17:49:46','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=160',157,'product','',0),(161,3,'2015-06-22 22:18:47','2015-06-22 22:18:47','The VTF clean room heating and drying ovens are available in six sizes with workspace volumes between 60 liters and 3,125 liters and with nominal 