:08','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?page_id=166',26,'page','',0),(167,4,'2015-06-22 22:33:51','2015-06-22 22:33:51','<h3>About Weiss Envirotronics</h3>\r\nOriginally established in 1979 for the purpose of servicing environmental test chambers, Weiss Envirotronics has become a leader in the design, manufacture, and service of environmental test equipment. We demand excellence in every aspect of our business, from our engineering capabilities and customer service to our manufacturing processes and personnel.\r\n\r\nThe production of high quality environmental test equipment is dependent upon several key factors including skilled personnel and a smooth production process. Weiss Envirotronics maintains the theory that investment in these critical resources ensures consistency in the design manufacture, and service of our products. We mandate training and education among our employees and insist that our facility and manufacturing processes are continually reviewed and upgraded.\r\n\r\nWe seek employees of the highest quality, whether they are seasoned in the business or simply possess the inherent attributes of diligence and drive. We retain our employees by fostering a unique corporate culture, where each person is valued regardless of position. The atmosphere at Weiss Envirotronics feels as though the company were still a small, family-operated business even though we have grown to employ more than 150 individuals in the USA and are part of Weiss which employs over 1,700 individuals around the world and part of the Schunk Group which employs over 8,250 individuals around the world. We  are established as a world-leader in the design, manufacture, and service of environmental test equipment.\r\n\r\nFor information on current openings › click on the links to the left or contact our Human Resources Department at: <i><a href=\"mailto:personnel@envirotronics.com\">personnel@envirotronics.com</a>\r\n</i>\r\n\r\n<i>Weiss Envirotronics is an equal opportunity employer.</i>\r\n\r\n<i>To apply for a position please fill out the attached <a href=\"http://envirotronics.com/wp-content/uploads/Employment_Application_Form_WENV_v52.pdf\">employment application</a>, save and email to personnel@envirotronics.com</i>','Careers','','publish','open','open','','careers','','','2015-08-14 17:36:12','2015-08-14 17:36:12','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?page_id=167',21,'page','',0),(169,4,'2015-06-22 22:34:08','2015-06-22 22:34:08','<h2>Contact Form</h2>\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"1951\" title=\"Contact form 1\"]','Contact','','publish','open','open','','contact','','','2015-08-11 17:29:43','2015-08-11 17:29:43','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?page_id=169',22,'page','',0),(170,4,'2015-06-22 22:36:45','2015-06-22 22:36:45',' ','','','publish','open','open','','170','','','2015-06-22 22:37:25','2015-06-22 22:37:25','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?p=170',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(171,4,'2015-06-22 22:36:45','2015-06-22 22:36:45',' ','','','publish','open','open','','171','','','2015-06-22 22:37:25','2015-06-22 22:37:25','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?p=171',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(172,4,'2015-06-22 22:36:45','2015-06-22 22:36:45',' ','','','publish','open','open','','172','','','2015-06-22 22:37:25','2015-06-22 22:37:25','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?p=172',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(173,4,'2015-06-22 22:36:45','2015-06-22 22:36:45',' ','','','publish','open','open','','173','','','2015-06-22 22:37:25','2015-06-22 22:37:25','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?p=173',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(174,4,'2015-06-22 22:36:14','2015-06-22 22:36:14','High safety standards worldwide, a high degree of reliability, modern workplaces and a cooperative environment are only a few of the factors that our employees value. We strive to foster the long-term loyalty of our employees and provide them with opportunities for continued growth so they are better able to meet the changing demands of our market. We are very aw