mber to meet your specific needs.</em></em>\r\n\r\n<em><span style=\"font-family: Times;\">*EAH models are constructed with an internal pressure member. EA Models can be quoted with an external pressure member construction.</span></em>','EA and EAH Series','','publish','closed','closed','','ea-and-eah-series','','','2015-07-31 20:10:48','2015-07-31 20:10:48','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=248',110,'product','',0),(249,3,'2015-06-23 17:22:45','2015-06-23 17:22:45','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Weiss Envirotronics altitude test chambers are designed based upon the specialized needs of the automobile industry and allow for a simulation of air pressure up to a height of 4000 meters. Regardless of location or season the combination of cold and climate allows for a broad range of test possibilities.</span></p>','Altitude Chill Climate','','publish','closed','closed','','altitude-chill-climate-2','','','2015-07-29 18:21:26','2015-07-29 18:21:26','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=249',111,'product','',0),(250,3,'2015-06-23 17:23:04','2015-06-23 17:23:04','The WT/D and WK/D vacuum-temperature and vacuum climate test chambers offer a way for reproducible tests of aviation industry components, are highly stressed.\r\nOur chambers allow the simulation of extreme flight programs in accordance with the relevant standards. For many years they have been applied in the fields of research, development, production and quality control.','WT-D/WK-D','','publish','closed','closed','','wt-dwk-d-2','','','2015-08-04 15:25:02','2015-08-04 15:25:02','',0,'http://envirotronics.wpengine.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=250',109,'product','',0),(251,3,'2015-06-23 17:24:52','2015-06-23 17:24:52','The Weiss Envirotronics Module-R type C-SP mobile air conditioning containers are a split system consisting of the evaporator module inside the unit, and the condenser unit outside. These two modules are connected by a quick release, 