ional Information.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>SC 450</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1928\" src=\"http://envirotronics.com/wp-content/uploads/SC-1000-offen.jpg.4226965.jpg\" alt=\"SC 1000 offen.jpg.4226965\" width=\"167\" height=\"111\" /></h3>\r\n<h3>Weiss  Salt Spray Corrosion Chamber available for immediate shipment.</h3>\r\nA new, in stock, SC 450 has the following features:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Corrosion Resistant housing made from recyclable polyethylene</li>\r\n	<li>Powerful 32-Bit S!MCON Touchscreen Controller</li>\r\n	<li>Digital set and actual value displays</li>\r\n	<li>Low Energy Requirements</li>\r\n	<li>Compact Design</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nContact Weiss Envirotronics at <a href=\"mailto:sales@envirotronics.com\">sales@envirotronics.com</a> or 1-800-368-4768 for Pricing, Shipping and Additional Information.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Star Series 36\" Vibration Table and Console\r\n1 Each\r\n<em>Star Series 36\" Vibration Table and Console\r\nNEW</em></h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1929 size-full\" src=\"http://envirotronics.com/wp-content/uploads/vib-table232.jpg\" alt=\"vib-table232\" width=\"232\" height=\"193\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Patented State-of-the-Art Six Degrees of Freedom, Tri-axial, Pneumatic Vibration Tables</li>\r\n	<li>Table can be used with or without test chamber</li>\r\n	<li>Large number of mounting holes allows greater flexibility in mounting your product</li>\r\n	<li>Table can be fitted into any AGREE chamber that can handle the physical size</li>\r\n	<li>Efficient air usage at average vibration levels keeps your operating costs low</li>\r\n	<li>Easy Lift actuator switch allows for easy operation</li>\r\n	<li>Table is on an easy to use Airfloat pneumatic guide system</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nContact Weiss Envirotronics at <a href=\"mailto:sales@envirotronics.com\">sales@envirotronics.com</a> or 1-800-368-4768 for Pricing, Shipping and Additional Information.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Weiss Envirotronics has one (1) FLX900 Tempe