ct Weiss Envirotronics at <a href=\"mailto:sales@envirotronics.com\">sales@envirotronics.com</a> or 1-800-368-4768 for Pricing, Shipping and Additional Information.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1929 size-full\" src=\"http://envirotronics.com/wp-content/uploads/vib-table232.jpg\" alt=\"vib-table232\" width=\"232\" height=\"193\" /></h3>\n<h3>Star Series 36\" Vibration Table and Console\n1 Each\n<em>Star Series 36\" Vibration Table and Console\nNEW</em></h3>\n<ul>\n	<li>Patented State-of-the-Art Six Degrees of Freedom, Tri-axial, Pneumatic Vibration Tables</li>\n	<li>Table can be used with or without test chamber</li>\n	<li>Large number of mounting holes allows greater flexibility in mounting your product</li>\n	<li>Table can be fitted into any AGREE chamber that can handle the physical size</li>\n	<li>Efficient air usage at average vibration levels keeps your operating costs low</li>\n	<li>Easy Lift actuator switch allows for easy operation</li>\n	<li>Table is on an easy to use Airfloat pneumatic guide system</li>\n</ul>\nContact Weiss Envirotronics at <a href=\"mailto:sales@envirotronics.com\">sales@envirotronics.com</a> or 1-800-368-4768 for Pricing, Shipping and Additional Information.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Weiss Envirotronics has one (1) FLX900 Temperature &amp; Humidity chamber available for immediate shipment!</strong>\n\nA new, in stock, FLX900-2-3.5-WC-H has the following features:\n<ul>\n	<li>Temperature Range: -73C to 177C</li>\n	<li>Workspace: 38″ Wide X 38″ Deep X 38″ High</li>\n	<li>Water-cooled refrigeration</li>\n	<li>2 each 50 lbs. shelves</li>\n	<li>Machine Quiet Package</li>\n	<li>5 CFM Dry Air Purge System</li>\n	<li>3 Additional Event Relays</li>\n	<li>Navigator Programmer/Controller</li>\n</ul>\nContact Weiss Envirotronics at <a href=\"mailto:sales@envirotronics.com\">sales@envirotronics.com</a> or 1-800-368-4768 for Pricing, Shipping and Additional Information.\n\n&nbsp;','In Stock Chambers - Ready to Ship','','inherit